This paper investigates the relationship between national policies around freedom of speech and Internet topology, which involves network measurement and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also touches upon issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CR), social and information networks (cs.SI), privacy and security (cs.CY), and performance analysis (cs.PF).
